  <div class="col-md-6">
	  
	  
	  <h3>African-American Families</h3>

<h4><a href="kinship/davis/">Davis Family Network</a></h4>

<p>Two generations of the Davis family petitioned the Court in D.C. for their freedom from various masters, including a member of the <a href="./fam.forrest.html">Forrest</a> family.</p>  

<h4><a href="kinship/lee/">Lee Family Network</a></h4>

<p>Two generations of the Lee family petitioned for their freedom in the Circuit Court in D.C.</p>
    
<h4><a href="kinship/queen/">Queen Family Network</a></h4>

<p>Many members of the Queen family petitioned courts in Maryland and D.C. for their freedom.</p>  
	  
	  
	  
